machine is set up from two different angles.  Then, both machines
emits a high intensity radiation which crosses the subjects'
brains.  Then bgth machines are also used to receive and interpret
the information collected from against side. When the subject,s
brain waves of detecting send to the CPU,it will be translated into
thoughts with words or picture, finally appears on the monitor
which operator can read & understand. 
