2.  It is not only harmful to your body, but it also can kill you.
    Whenever this machine is being operated on high frequency, it
can be used to kill you.  The beam of high frequency radiation
emitted from the machine can be aimed at your head or your body. 
If the target is your head, your central nervous system will be
damaged.  If the target is your body, your organs will be damaged. 
